 known as eh holding corporation and changed its name to hughes satellite systems corporation in october  the company was founded in  and is headquartered in englewood colorado hughes satellite systems corporation is a subsidiary of echostar corporation detailed description  inverness terrace eastenglewood co united statesfounded in  phone  key executives for hughes satellite systems corporation mr michael t dugan chief executive officer president and director age  mr david j rayner chief financial officer principal accounting officer executive vice president and treasurer age  mr bernard l han executive vice president of dish network age  mr dean a manson executive vice president general counsel secretary and director age  mr r stanton dodge esq executive vice president general counsel and secretary of echostar satellite services llc age  compensation as of fiscal year  hughes satellite systems corporation key developments hughes satellite systems corporation announces issuance of  million aggregate principal amount of its  senior secured notes due  jul   on july   hughes satellite systems corporation hssc a subsidiary of echostar corporation entered into an indenture the secured indenture among hssc the guarantors named on the signature pages thereto the guarantors us bank national association as trustee the trustee and wells fargo bank national association as collateral agent the collateral agent relating to hsscs issuance of  million aggregate principal amount of its  senior secured notes due  the secured notes at an issue price of  on the same date hssc also entered into an indenture the unsecured indenture and together with the secured indenture the indentures among hssc the guarantors and the trustee relating to hsscs issuance of  million aggregate principal amount of its  senior notes due  at an issue price of  the unsecured notes and together with the secured notes the notes on july   hssc issued  million aggregate principal amount of secured notes pursuant